title: "missdetect: Hierarchical Classification of Missing-Data Mechanisms with Statistical and LLM-Augmented Features"
message: "If you use this software or the accompanying experiments, please cite both the software and the master's thesis."
type: software
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-05-03"
